name: LILITH
description: The person I photographed is my mother and she is the strongest woman I have ever known in my life. She represents Lilith in mythology who is known as demonic female figure from the male gaze but she rejects all the adjectives from their POV. My mother, as Lilith, runs after her freedom and loved ones by resisting all kinds of restrictions and possessions. Lilith is my mother who made me who I am.
